title: Secure In His Sovereignty | Joel Osteen

description:
God has favor prepared for you that can’t be overridden. When it’s His sovereign will for you to be blessed, nothing can keep you from the blessings He has planned for you.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
